{
  "stem": "18056.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was picked, and another fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to sit on his head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he [INAUDIBLE] in 25 into him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then-- fortunately, he broke his-- his-- his whip.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and then the other guy was sitting on my head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got mine-- that for about six weeks, I couldn't even lay on my back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was-- I was ruined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is basically the only thing they did for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were nice enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- the manager of the-- of that-- of our camp-- you know, I went there and I told them the story what happened.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I said, I didn't do it, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he called one of the Kapos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, when you go back to work tonight, you make sure that he goes into-- we had, like, a hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If somebody got injured on the job or stuff like this, they was able to let him rest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For about a week, I didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I got there, the men knew that I was injured because my back was-- was blue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for about a week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for six weeks, I couldn't lay on the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a German-- one of the German-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of the Germans that did it, yeah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The soldiers, the-- the Wehrmacht, the regular German soldiers-- that's the ones who would communicate with us because as we walked to work, they were the ones that would-- on-- on the sides, they would walk and talk to us a little bit.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would say, the Germans are losing and all this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to give us a little hope that we are still alive or that we will survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
